item.title: 2017-02-28 ELK? aws and openvpn
item.description: ELK There is this thing called elk, and I have no idea how to use it. I don’t even know where to being with ELK. I have been using splunk for years, I know how ot do all of this in splunk. But because the data I need is in elk and i cannot easily get it in to splunk I will have to at least start with elk and then go from there.
